<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-11179] JSR308 inline constants for annotations in class header</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-11179</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Consider the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
@Tag(value=C.VALUE)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;C&amp;lt;@Tag(value=C.VALUE) T&amp;gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; @Tag(value=C.VALUE) &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;implements&lt;/span&gt; @Tag(value=C.VALUE) Serializable
{
  public static final &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; VALUE = &quot;&quot;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//...
&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Annotations located in the class header are processed before &lt;tt&gt;VariableScopeVisitor&lt;/tt&gt; (in &lt;tt&gt;ResolveVisitor&lt;/tt&gt;).  Only the annotation in &lt;tt&gt;C&lt;/tt&gt; properly resolves &quot;C&quot; and its constant field &quot;VALUE&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
